hmacMD5.desc: Calculates an HMAC using a key and an MD5 hash
hmacMD5.doc:
Calculates an HMAC using a key and an MD5 hash

Parameters:
 * key - A string containing a secret key to use
 * data - A string containing the data to hash

Returns:
 * A string containing the hash of the supplied data
hmacMD5.name: hmacMD5
parameters: * key - A string containing a secret key to use
* data - A string containing the data to hash
returns: * A string containing the hash of the supplied data
